snippet.title: Summer Trip Cruise - Alpha Trailer | Wishlist now on Steam!
snippet.description:
Summer Trip Cruise is a game about driving a cruise through the seas and make the tourist have the best holiday of their lives.

This is an alpha trailer, so expect changes and more content to come out over the next few months. The game will be released on Q4 2022 on Steam if no unexpected stuff happens.

▶Wishlist on Steam! - https://store.steampowered.com/app/2103480/Summer_Trip_Cruise/

🎺Summer Trip Cruise music by J.L.Chinchilla - https://jlchinchillamusic.wixsite.com/composer
